## Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/mateusbentes/proof.git
cd proof
cp .env.example .env
docker-compose up -d
# Visit http://localhost:3000
```

## Technology Stack

- Backend: Node.js, Express, PostgreSQL, Rasa
- Frontend: React 18, Zustand, Axios
- Infrastructure: Docker, Docker Compose
- Security: JWT, bcryptjs, Helmet, CORS

